{
  "stem": "23626.2",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "All of a sudden, I felt a pull from the back, by my braids, and a slap on my cheek that everything swirled in front of me.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I started to cry.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And he hit me once more, even harder.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "He says, in my house, I don't want see any sad faces.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Do you understand?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And from a distance, I saw my friend shaking her head.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "You know?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Your-- the other--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Helen, yeah, the other Helen.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "She was-- she saw-- I guess she knew him already for those few weeks.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "She was older.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "She was, I think, 12, 14 years older than me.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "She spoke fluently German.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I had to learn the hard way.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "She helped me a lot.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "She taught me a lot, because she knew how to iron a shirt by then.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I learned so fast.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I grew up so fast, because I had to.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Because when he said to me, in my house, I don't want to see sad faces, and in Austria, a girl your age knows how to iron a shirt properly, but you too stupid.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "You are a Jew.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I had to learn.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Because if I didn't learn, I was getting so much beating.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Under the slightest provocation, I received the most cruel punishment.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] You know that I remember my ears most of the time ringing.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I always had the ringing in my ears.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Because he would slap me on the slightest provocation.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "If I wouldn't look straight in his face, if I-- if he talked to me and I would look sideways, there it was.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And how many times I rolled down those stairs in the villa later, that I am surprised that I only have this condition in my neck that I found out later.",
      "word_count": 31
    }
  ],
